title: Alan Moore Collection II-  DC
description:
So this is me breaking apart my Massive 29 gig Alan Moore Collection into much easier to to download pieces. 

This torrent is only a bit over 1 gigs and has all the comics Alan Moore wrote before coming to America

Titles include Batman, Detective Comics, Green Arrow, Black Cannery, Green Lantern, Omega Men, Superman, Swamp Thing, The Phantom Stranger, Vigilante, & V For Vendetta

All comics ripped from a printing of Alan Moore's DC Universe with the exception of Secret Origin #010- The Phantom Stranger which includes work not written by Alan Moore for the full effect of the origin of The Phantom Stranger

If you are wondering where Watchmen is it get's it's own torrent you just wait.

Please enjoy. Please please please donate to this Kickstarter
